    Frequently asked questions

    Can I customize my productivity app after it's created?

    Yes, you can! You can refine your app using AI chat or Visual Edit to add pages, workflows, and design tweaks.

    How do I get started building productivity apps?

    To start building productivity apps, simply give Base44 plain-language prompts. Your app deploys live instantly and you can refine it to your liking.

    Which integrations can I add to my productivity apps?

    You can connect external tools through the catalog or AI chat. API keys are stored as secrets, and backend functions enable custom APIs.

    Can I build productivity apps without coding experience?

    Absolutely! Base44 is designed to build apps from plain-language prompts, so you don't need any coding experience.

    Can I build productivity apps for free?

    Yes, you can build productivity apps for free. However, features like custom domains, integrations, and exporting require a Builder or higher plan.

    How do I build productivity apps with AI?

    You can build productivity apps with AI by giving plain-language prompts to Base44. It constructs full-stack apps that deploy live instantly. You can then refine your app using AI chat or Visual Edit.

    So, what are we building?

    Get started

    Base44 is the AI-powered platform that lets users build fully functioning apps in minutes. Using nothing but natural language, Base44 enables anyone to turn their words into personal productivity apps, back-office tools, customer portals, or complete enterprise products that are ready to use, no integrations required.
